                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.01 Provisional/6: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Counselor of Embassy in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Lockhart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-12-15T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 15, 1937—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>400. Your 825, December 14, 6 p.m.</p>
                <list>
                    <label>1.</label>
                    <item>You should be guided primarily by the necessity of avoiding action or
                        attitude that might be construed as carrying any degree of official
                        recognition of the new régime.</item>
                    <pb facs="0819" n="812" xml:id="pg_812"/>
                    <label>2.</label>
                    <item>Bearing in mind, however, the possible future practical need of informal
                        dealings with officials of the new régime in the protection of American
                        interests, the Department suggests that you receive any call made upon you
                        by persons representing the new régime and acknowledge such call by sending
                        or if deemed definitely expedient taking in return your personal card with
                        the personal name of your caller written upon it. You should avoid formal
                        relationships and keep your contacts on an informal, personal basis.</item>
                </list>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
